02:36.239 --> 02:38.199
to invite someone else.

02:38.241 --> 02:41.411
Well, Malcolm, I'm sorry

02:38.241 --> 02:41.411
that my mother's sister--

02:41.453 --> 02:44.289
the woman who took care of me

02:41.453 --> 02:44.289
every day after school--

02:44.331 --> 02:46.374
had to die and inconvenience

02:46.416 --> 02:47.668
your social life.

02:47.709 --> 02:49.419
She does it on purpose.

02:49.461 --> 02:53.214
