02:49.461 --> 02:53.214
different escape plans,

02:53.256 --> 02:56.343
but now my brain

02:53.256 --> 02:56.343
is filled with mom guilt.

03:05.268 --> 03:06.603
Who's this?

03:06.645 --> 03:08.271
