03:17.156 --> 03:18.615
Uh-huh.

03:17.156 --> 03:18.615
Who is he?

03:18.657 --> 03:19.658
I don't know.

03:21.785 --> 03:23.954
What's your name, son?

03:26.289 --> 03:27.248
