03:26.289 --> 03:27.248
Egg.

03:27.290 --> 03:28.625
Did he say Greg?

03:28.667 --> 03:30.544
I thought he said Craig.

03:30.585 --> 03:32.253
His name is Egg.

03:32.295 --> 03:34.882
"Egg"?

03:32.295 --> 03:34.882
I named him.

03:34.923 --> 03:36.424
Well, you can't keep him.

03:36.466 --> 03:38.886
He needs to go home, okay?

03:38.927 --> 03:41.471
Okay.

03:41.513 --> 03:43.140
This stinks.

03:43.182 --> 03:45.433
Whether it's a wedding,

03:43.182 --> 03:45.433
a funeral or court date,

03:45.475 --> 03:47.477
these family gatherings

03:45.475 --> 03:47.477
are always the same.

03:47.519 --> 03:50.480
Ooh! I just can't take

03:47.519 --> 03:50.480
my hands off that face!

03:50.522 --> 03:52.816
(women clamoring)

03:54.526 --> 03:56.528
I can't wait till I get zits.

03:56.570 --> 03:58.739
At least then I can fight back.

03:58.780 --> 04:00.448
Hal, you have to get ready.

04:00.490 --> 04:02.951
Why are you still messing around

04:00.490 --> 04:02.951
with those record albums?

04:02.993 --> 04:05.286
Well, I thought I was gonna

04:02.993 --> 04:05.286
spend today in the garage

04:05.328 --> 04:07.288
listening to them

04:05.328 --> 04:07.288
on my quadraphonic.

04:07.330 --> 04:08.289
But now that we're going

04:07.330 --> 04:08.289
to the funeral,

04:08.331 --> 04:10.291
I have to reseal

04:08.331 --> 04:10.291
the shrink wrap.

04:10.333 --> 04:11.292
Hal!

04:10.333 --> 04:11.292
I'll hurry, okay?

04:11.334 --> 04:12.794
I have to get

04:11.334 --> 04:12.794
my speech ready anyway.

04:12.836 --> 04:14.796
Honey, you know

04:12.836 --> 04:14.796
you don't have to talk

04:14.838 --> 04:16.297
at every funeral we go to.

04:16.339 --> 04:17.758
Whew, I wish that were true.

04:17.799 --> 04:19.300
You see how people look to me

04:19.342 --> 04:21.386
when they ask if somebody has

04:19.342 --> 04:21.386
a few words to say?

04:21.428 --> 04:23.471
They're not looking to you,

04:21.428 --> 04:23.471
they're looking at you.

04:23.513 --> 04:25.390
To, at... what's

04:23.513 --> 04:25.390
the difference?

