Hello.

04:30.353 --> 04:32.147
Hey, Mom, I'm just warning you,

04:32.189 --> 04:34.315
someone claiming to be the

04:32.189 --> 04:34.315
commandant might call you soon.

04:34.357 --> 04:35.817
It's just this guy

04:34.357 --> 04:35.817
down the hall.

04:35.859 --> 04:37.402
Just play along and pretend

04:35.859 --> 04:37.402
you believe him.

04:37.444 --> 04:39.113
He's totally harmless.

04:39.154 --> 04:40.488
Francis, I really can't

04:39.154 --> 04:40.488
talk to you right now.

04:40.530 --> 04:42.574
We're on our way

04:40.530 --> 04:42.574
to Aunt Helen's funeral.

04:42.616 --> 04:44.785
Aunt Helen died?

04:44.826 --> 04:46.536
Well, I sure hope so.

04:44.826 --> 04:46.536
We're going to her funeral.

04:46.578 --> 04:47.996
Well, when did she die?

04:48.038 --> 04:49.039
Mom, why didn't

04:48.038 --> 04:49.039
anybody tell me?!

04:49.081 --> 04:50.331
Uh, well, honey, we just,

04:50.373 --> 04:52.542
we didn't want to have

04:50.373 --> 04:52.542
