05:50.517 --> 05:52.393
I think so. Why?

05:52.435 --> 05:55.438
Because I'm going to stash

05:52.435 --> 05:55.438
this with Aunt Helen.

05:55.480 --> 05:57.107
What is that?

05:57.149 --> 05:58.608
It's a Mighty Man.

05:57.149 --> 05:58.608
Mom and Dad had it

05:58.650 --> 06:00.485
in the back of their closet

05:58.650 --> 06:00.485
for some reason.

06:00.527 --> 06:02.237
I'm Mighty Man.

06:00.527 --> 06:02.237
It's Dewey's

06:00.527 --> 06:02.237
birthday next week.

06:02.279 --> 06:03.404
This is his present.

06:03.446 --> 06:05.824
Oh.

06:03.446 --> 06:05.824
What'd you do to it?

06:05.866 --> 06:08.118
I stomped on it.

06:05.866 --> 06:08.118
Why would you do that?

06:08.160 --> 06:11.496
Look, I don't know why

06:08.160 --> 06:11.496
I do the things I do.

06:11.538 --> 06:13.414
I just know I don't

06:11.538 --> 06:13.414
want to get caught.

06:13.456 --> 06:15.583
That's why Aunt Helen

06:13.456 --> 06:15.583
is getting a new friend.

06:15.625 --> 06:17.585
You're gonna bury

06:15.625 --> 06:17.585
that with her?

06:17.627 --> 06:18.670
You are so dead.

06:18.712 --> 06:20.130
Hey, I watch lawyer shows.

06:20.172 --> 06:21.506
Mom will think I did it,

06:21.548 --> 06:23.424
but she can't prove it

06:21.548 --> 06:23.424
without this.

06:23.466 --> 06:25.010
It's in the Constitution--

06:25.052 --> 06:26.427
no evidence, no conviction.

06:26.469 --> 06:28.638
E pluribus unum.

06:33.894 --> 06:35.729
(chuckling):

06:33.894 --> 06:35.729
Oh, yeah.

06:35.770 --> 06:37.105
Hi, honey.

06:35.770 --> 06:37.105
Hey, you know,

06:37.147 --> 06:38.523
I finally found my joke cards.

06:38.565 --> 06:40.441
For some reason, they were

06:38.565 --> 06:40.441
behind the water heater.

06:40.483 --> 06:42.443
Really?

06:40.483 --> 06:42.443
Hey, how's this?

06:42.485 --> 06:44.321
"A priest, a rabbi

06:42.485 --> 06:44.321
and Uncle Fred are..."

06:44.363 --> 06:45.488
Oh, well, Aunt Helen.

06:45.530 --> 06:47.324
"...are playing golf

06:45.530 --> 06:47.324
with Saint Peter."

06:47.366 --> 06:49.659
Hal, please!

06:47.366 --> 06:49.659
Hey, have you seen

06:47.366 --> 06:49.659
my pun file?

06:49.701 --> 06:52.204
It's in a box marked

06:49.701 --> 06:52.204
"laughter thoughts."

06:54.164 --> 06:55.414
Laughter thoughts?

06:58.335 --> 07:00.503
(whistles)

07:00.545 --> 07:03.131
How did she die?

07:00.545 --> 07:03.131
Cats ate her face.

07:03.173 --> 07:05.717
Dewey, I think you're confused.

07:03.173 --> 07:05.717
I'm asking about Aunt Helen.

07:05.759 --> 07:07.468
Cats ate her face.

07:05.759 --> 07:07.468
Look, would you just

07:07.510 --> 07:08.762
put Mom or Dad on the phone?

07:10.347 --> 07:11.556
Hello.

07:10.347 --> 07:11.556
Dad!

07:11.598 --> 07:13.308
What happened to Aunt Helen?

07:13.350 --> 07:14.559
Cats ate her face.

07:14.601 --> 07:16.811
Well, here, Dewey knows

07:14.601 --> 07:16.811
